import React from 'react'
import { Container,Row,Col } from 'react-bootstrap'

function footer() {
    return (
        
            <footer>
                <Container>
                    <Row>
                        <Col className= 'text-center py-3'>
                        Copyright © Ecommerce Web
                        </Col>
                    </Row>
                </Container>
            </footer>
        
    )
}

export default footer
